4. If you mail your absentee ballot, it must be postmarked by Election Day & received by your county clerk before the Canvass begins. Plan to mail or hand-deliver your absentee ballot to your County Clerk's office in time. Track your absentee ballot here: services.sos.wv.gov/Elections/Vote…
1. Register to vote online, by mail, or at your County Clerk's office, or check the status of your voter registration: ovr.sos.wv.gov/Register/Landi… The deadline to register and be eligible to vote in the 2020 General Election is close of business on October 13.
